
Taken from

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/14924247/how-to-print-convert-decimal-floating-point-values-in-gcc

This example requires libdfp

https://github.com/libdfp/libdfp

Debian sources for constructing a Debian package

https://salsa.debian.org/debian/libdfp.git

We need explicit linking with this library for printf to work.

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11631161/force-to-link-against-unused-shared-library
